The paper discusses a method for video recognition using deep learning techniques, specifically Deep Belief Networks and Long Short Term Memory. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of adaptive structural learning, which falls under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also mentions the use of LSTM for time-series analysis, which falls under the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
